    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>Sådan er reglerne for nødbelysningsanlæg</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Læs her hvilke ledningssystemer, herunder skinner, som kan anvendes til nødbelysningsanlæg. Nødbelysningsanlæg kan enten laves som en traditionel fast installation eller et armatursystem der markedsføres som et produkt.
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Global/Publikationer/Artikler/OEvrige-artikler/2015/Saadan-er-reglerne-for-noedbelysningsanlaeg" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Global/Publikationer/Artikler/OEvrige-artikler/2015/Saadan-er-reglerne-for-noedbelysningsanlaeg" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Global/Publikationer/Artikler/OEvrige-artikler/2015/Saadan-er-reglerne-for-noedbelysningsanlaeg" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Global/Publikationer/Artikler/OEvrige-artikler/2015/Saadan-er-reglerne-for-noedbelysningsanlaeg" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Sådan er reglerne for nødbelysningsanlæg&body=https://sik.dk/Global/Publikationer/Artikler/OEvrige-artikler/2015/Saadan-er-reglerne-for-noedbelysningsanlaeg" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Traditionel fast installation</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Denne type nødbelysningsanlæg skal udføres af en autoriseret virksomhed indenfor el og skal udføres i&nbsp;overensstemmelse med stærkstrømsbekendtgørelsen afsnit 6, kapitel 805, nødbelysning og varslingsanlæg.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ledningssystemer i elektriske installationer for nødbelysning skal overholde SB afs. 6, 805.521</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Et ledningssystem er defineret i SB afs. 6, 216.1:&nbsp;216.1 Ledningssystem.&nbsp;En eller flere ledninger eller skinner med fastgørelsesmateriel og eventuel kapsling.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Specifikt for ledningssystemer der anvendes til nødbelysning og varslingsanlæg angives i SB afs. 6, 805.521:&nbsp;Kun følgende ledningssystemer må anvendes:</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Brandsikre kabler som opfylder IEC 60331</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Mineralisolerede kabler.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Varmebestandig siliconegummiisoleret monteringsledning type H05SJ-K i rør. I skjult&nbsp;installation i brændbare bygningsdele og overalt i synlig installation skal der anvendes&nbsp;metalrør.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Andre egnede ledninger eller kabler efter særlig tilladelse fra Elektricitetsrådet.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

Note I varslingsanlæg udstyret med nød- eller reserveforsyning stilles ingen særlige krav til&nbsp;ledningssystemer foran nød- eller reserveforsyningsenheden.<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Ledningssystemerne skal anbringes således, at de under en brand kan opretholde&nbsp;strømforsyningen så længe som muligt.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Af hensyn til risikoen for trækbelastninger i ledningssystemet i løbet af den krævede&nbsp;funktionstid må ledninger ikke fastgøres til bygningsdele af brændbart materiale.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ved samling af brandsikre kabler i dåser af plast o.l. skal der anvendes klemmer med hus af&nbsp;porcelæn. Hvis inderlederne i det brandsikre kabel ikke er brandsikre, skal de forsynes med&nbsp;en brandsikker strømpe eller med brandsikkert tape.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

I forbindelsen mellem et selvstændigt hovedarmatur for nødbelysning og et sattelitarmatur må&nbsp;der højst være et spændingsfald på 3 %. Den største ledningslængde, som begrænser<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
spændingsfaldet til 3%, er angivet i den brugsanvisning, der følger med armaturet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det fremgår således at skinner, herunder kontaktskinner (DS/EN60570) og kanalskinner (DS/EN61439-6),&nbsp;ikke må anvendes i elektriske installationer for nødbelysning og varslingsanlæg.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Armatursystem der markedsføres som et produkt</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Denne type nødbelysningsanlæg kan udføres af alle fabrikanter og skal overholde Lavspændingsdirektivet,&nbsp;herunder CE-mærkes.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Fabrikanten er ansvarlig for at det samlede system overholder de vigtigste sikkerhedskrav for elektrisk&nbsp;materiel i henhold til Lavspændingsdirektivet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Overholdelsen af de vigtigste sikkerhedskrav for elektrisk materiel i henhold til Lavspændingsdirektivet kan&nbsp;fx ske ved overholdelse af relevante harmoniserede standarder.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Såfremt det vælges at overholde relevante harmoniserede standarder kan fabrikanten formode at vigtigste&nbsp;sikkerhedskrav for elektrisk materiel er overholdt.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Såfremt det ikke vælges at overholde relevante harmoniserede standarder mistes formodningsretten.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I øvrigt henvises til:</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="http://ec.europa.eu/growth/sectors/electrical-engineering/lvd-directive/index_en.htm" title="Link til Low Voltage Directive - Guidelines on application and recommendations" target="_self">Low Voltage Directive - Guidelines on application and recommendations</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="http://ec.europa.eu/growth/single-market/goods/index_en.htm" title="Link til The ‘Blue Guide’ on the implementation of EU product rules" target="_self">The ‘Blue Guide’ on the implementation of EU product rules</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Se fx: 4.1.2. CONFORMITY WITH THE ESSENTIAL REQUIREMENTS: HARMONISED STANDARDS&nbsp;4.1.3. CONFORMITY WITH THE ESSENTIAL REQUIREMENTS: OTHER POSSIBILITIES</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ovenstående forhindrer således ikke at fx kontaktskinner indgår som en del af et armatursystem der&nbsp;anvendes til nødbelysning. Forudsætningen er at kontaktskinnerne markedsføres som del af et samlet&nbsp;system hvor fabrikanten erklærer at det samlede system er egnet og beregnet til nødbelysning, samt&nbsp;foretager CE-mærkning i henhold til Lavspændingsdirektivet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Specifikt for belysningsarmaturer, herunder systemarmatur, der anvendes til nødbelysning angives i&nbsp;stærkstrømsbekendtgørelsen afs. 6, 805.56 at disse også skal opfylde bestemmelserne i EN60598-2-22.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Den elektriske installation der skal forsyne armatursystemet skal udføres af en autoriseret virksomhed&nbsp;indenfor el og skal udføres i overensstemmelse med stærkstrømsbekendtgørelsen afsnit 6 kapitel 56,&nbsp;nødforsyning, samt kapitel 805, nødbelysning og varslingsanlæg.</p>
